<L>__{exterior fields day}
<A>__{beyond samuel, well out in the fields of the stoltzfus farm, stotlzfus and others including hochstetler and his brothers are baling the first cutting of june hay. but the operation has come to a halt. all are looking in toward the lapp farm, hearing the ringing of the bell (the amish cry for help), wondering, hesitating. but now, as we watch, led by hochstetler, they start in toward samuel.}
